                     <interp inst="t18451027-2003-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="fraud"></interp> for unlawfully obtaining by false pretences, 1 hat, value 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18451027-name-388" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18451027-name-388" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
